### Add a document
POST http://ec2-63-177-72-122.eu-central-1.compute.amazonaws.com/api/training/demo/v1/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic c3VwZXJ1c2VyOlNZUw==

{
    "text": "InterSystems IRIS supports native vector storage with HNSW indexing", 
    "metadata": {
        "source": "docs"
        }
}

### Similarity search
POST http://ec2-63-177-72-122.eu-central-1.compute.amazonaws.com/api/training/demo/v1/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic c3VwZXJ1c2VyOlNZUw==

{"query": "vector database features", "k": 5}

### List all documents

GET http://ec2-63-177-72-122.eu-central-1.compute.amazonaws.com/api/training/demo/v1/documents
Authorization: Basic c3VwZXJ1c2VyOlNZUw==

### Delete a document (replace <uid> with actual uid from add response)

DELETE http://ec2-63-177-72-122.eu-central-1.compute.amazonaws.com/api/training/demo/v1/documents/<uid>
Authorization: Basic c3VwZXJ1c2VyOlNZUw==
